data.description: Looking for a home just a 10 minute drive  away from Key West. This is it! This home is the perfect property for you. This 3 bedroom 2 bath stilt one story home. Built just 4 years ago in excellent condition.  The primary bedroom offers a walk-in closet and a walk in shower enclosure.  The kitchen features, stainless steel appliances, Corian countertops,    great natural lighting, crown moulding throughout. Plenty of storage, laundry room with LG washer and Dryer. Elevated home for safety and lower insurance costs, this home boast a sturdy metal roof which enhances energy efficiency.A Porch and Balcony in the front and a patio deck in the back yard, with nice  yard that has plenty of space to add a pool,. Lots of yard with ample room of parking space for an RV with Hook Up already in place, and still have an plenty  space for all of your water toys!A Covered Carport that fits 2 vehicles under covered space and a storage shed included. Bring your boat and launch it at the  public boat ramp just down the way!Don't miss the chance to be just minutes away from the vibrant energy of Key West yet find your sanctuary of comfort and tranquility awaits in your new home.Call Today!
